Package gameClient.GameData

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    the main Agent just Extends some version
    AgentBasic
    Base Agent, implements all the basic functions that we share with all agents
    AgentV1
    Version 1 of the agent, uses straight forward path finding
    AgentVG
    Version 2 of agent uses Groups of pokemons and path finding a.k.a its smarter
    GameData
    class that reads the server data and transform it into a readable class
    PokaGroup
    A Group of pokemons that are on the same edge, also getting connected to adjacent groups
    PokaGroupCreator
    Manager for PokaGroups, its responsible for updating everything related to pokemons
    Pokemon
    Pokemon data implementation
    PokemonGameData
    This is the GameManager, holding all the data, and handling server updates
